+# ProjectV2 user-owned view endpoint correction
+
+## Observed API behavior
+
+```text
+users/58338908/projectsV2/3/views
+â 404 Not Found
+
+users/newicody/projectsV2/3/views
+â endpoint recognized
+â 422 for missing name/layout
+```
+
+For a user-owned ProjectV2 view, the reconciler must therefore use:
+
+```text
+users/{owner}/projectsV2/{number}/views
+```
+
+The numeric `user_id` remains in the preview report for diagnostics and
+correlation, but it is not used to construct the view mutation endpoint.
+
+## Deployment sequence
+
+```text
+Autodoc template corrected
+â copy only reconcile_projectv2_configuration.py to newicody/projects
+â run preview again
+â confirm the new plan_digest
+â execute view creation
+â configure group_by/column_field manually where reported
+```
